1. *Sreli* smo se prošle nedelje. (We met last week.)
2. Nasmejala me je njena reč koju je *srela* usput. (Her word she said on her way made me laugh.)
3. Ona se *srela* s njim pre nekoliko godina. (She met him a few years ago.)
4. Oni su se *sreli* u parku. (They met in the park.)
5. Nismo se očekivano *sreli*. (We did not meet unexpectedly.)